Context: Jack and Taylor are father and daughter duo 
who got caught between virus outbreak in their city,
they are on run for survival from infected people
who got affected by virus and finding their long lost relatives
in hope of family reunion/supplies. 

Objective: Jack meet his old colleague Lucy 
who was a friend of Jack's brother {Mark}.
In exchange of Mark's location, Jack has to completed one task for her.
Not a week ago, Lucy was looking for supplies or any survivors then out of nowhere.
Lucy and her camp buddies got attacked by few armed men.
Lucy wants Jack to investigate on this matter and find any information on who those men where? 

